params.name: loss
params.description: Classification loss as the sum of start token, end token (and is_impossible if provided) classificationlosses.

params.name: start_top_log_probs
params.description: Log probabilities for the top config.start_n_top start token possibilities (beam-search).

params.name: start_top_index
params.description: Indices for the top config.start_n_top start token possibilities (beam-search).

params.name: end_top_log_probs
params.description: Log probabilities for the top config.start_n_top * config.end_n_top end token possibilities(beam-search).

params.name: end_top_index
params.description: Indices for the top config.start_n_top * config.end_n_top end token possibilities (beam-search).

params.name: cls_logits
params.description: Log probabilities for the is_impossible label of the answers.
